Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.28,0:00:16.41,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,While just passing by,\NSuddenly we meet {めぐりあい　すれちがう}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:25.25,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Just like headlights of this familiar city \NThat come and go {この都会(まち)を行き交う　Headlight}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:28.34,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Once you had a dream {貴方の夢　}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.13,0:00:32.60,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,That I failed to live up to {冷たくかわした}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:37.60,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,To this day, I repent of what I did {あの時の私を　悔やんでしまう}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.98,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,During the times we spent together {unsure, maybe "back then, I was mourning"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:49.43,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Ah, once upon a time, \NWhen the fate brought us all together {Ah once upon a time　人は誰もみんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:58.95,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,That was not to make us hurt each other {傷付く為に　出逢う訳じゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:03.67,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Thank you for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:11.26,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Even if we had to part once, \NWe'll meet again somewhere {何処かで逢えると　別れたけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.26,0:01:15.76,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,I came to realize -
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:18.89,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Until the end of times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:29.90,Default,OP Trans,0,0,0,,Friends or lovers once \NCan never return to being them again {友達にも　恋人にも　戻れない事だけ　分かっていた}
