Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:25.43,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Driving down the midnight highway {真夜中の Highway}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.39,0:23:29.83,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Crossing through my memories {横切ってゆく Memories}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:33.79,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Just tonight, I ask you to be silent {ただ黙ったままあの日}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:37.82,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Eye to eye, we stare at each other {Eye と Eye 見つめてた}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:42.53,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Some nostalgic love song {懐かしい Love song}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.36,0:23:46.24,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Slowly flowing out from the radio {流れた From the radio}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.76,0:23:51.33,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,It's like fighting back {閉じこめた悲しみを　叩くように}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:57.92,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,this sadness, that's been locked away for long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.92,0:24:00.38,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Oh baby play for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.38,0:24:04.44,Default,ED Trans,0,0,0,,Soul music \NSweet soul music
